{"tid":534056,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]火影忍者 疾風亂舞 (106) PVP 士打鐸！","createTime":"2018-01-19T12:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T12:07:45.000Z","uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9a3e0bf27b4bc6a7e596624a180d165ec0a1fa","tid":534056,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>官網</strong> (附ios/an下載點) <br />\n<a href=\"http://narucole.jp/?at=1l3vkMx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnarucole.jp%2F%3Fat%3D1l3vkMx&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=3b52c3aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://narucole.jp/?at=1l3vkMx</a> <br />\n<strong>官方email address</strong><br />\nnarucole@help.gree.net <br />\n<br />\n<strong>官方宣傳GAMEPLAY</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M4fkx4Fu1uM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM4fkx4Fu1uM&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=30825e97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M4fkx4Fu1uM</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>攻略Wiki</strong> (日文,唔update): <br />\n<a href=\"http://naruto.upwiki.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnaruto.upwiki.net%2F&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=441a72ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://naruto.upwiki.net/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>本post吉祥物</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WA94W0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WA94W0.jpg&h=1d99f3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9k4RbFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9k4RbFA.jpg&h=13546ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>人人一抽入魂中新限</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>新手須知</strong><br />\n1. 入關前可以禁＂？＂(概要)，睇下打呢關有咩獎勵/用咩角會有特效(point+傷害)。<br />\n2.  <strong>&quot;報酬詳細&quot;</strong> : 每關都可以係揀任果到詳細睇有乜送。<span style=\"color: red;\">補充：有時Ｓ評級／打多幾次獎勵會更多。</span><br />\n3. <strong>&quot;攻略情報&quot;</strong> : 關於boss嘅弱點/無效技能、行動(例如幾時會用大技)、弱體同異常狀態有冇效等。<span style=\"color: red;\">補充：好重要，如果ｂｏｓｓ雷遁無效，你用招雷遁技本身傷害幾高都扣唔到佢血。</span><br />\n4. <strong>商店-交換所</strong> : 可以交換素材, 換友情point, 買製造忍具嘅書(買1次永久用, 但部份忍具書要打任先送) <span style=\"color: red;\">補充：每個月都可以用忍幣換石，最多25粒記得換! 忍幣可以靠賣野強化醒覺打關拎到。</span><br />\n5. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>高登好友list </strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uAP04wns2J2RzrySxJkggFqKv4B13npf2R1UDp6Z7tE/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1uAP04wns2J2RzrySxJkggFqKv4B13npf2R1UDp6Z7tE%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=c25694dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uAP04wns2J2RzrySxJkggFqKv4B13npf2R1UDp6Z7tE/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>巴打製角色評價</strong>(outdated<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qsLMB9lRO4EKuZ3GTwAFq4oG6J8Mtp5mTmgX-rQUa7c/pub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1qsLMB9lRO4EKuZ3GTwAFq4oG6J8Mtp5mTmgX-rQUa7c%2Fpub&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=553e5023\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qsLMB9lRO4EKuZ3GTwAFq4oG6J8Mtp5mTmgX-rQUa7c/pub</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>巴打新製角色評價(持續更新)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XpwrsjgyAy2D__uXclKX5HD2qJQWiT55Ib9LThSA5ug/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1XpwrsjgyAy2D__uXclKX5HD2qJQWiT55Ib9LThSA5ug%2Fedit&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=efda85a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XpwrsjgyAy2D__uXclKX5HD2qJQWiT55Ib9LThSA5ug/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>課金注意事項 </strong><br />\n用日本itunes下載遊戲再轉地區做香港課金, 會出現遊戲更新唔到嘅情況, 所以最好都係買日本itunes卡<br />\n<br />\n<strong>刷首抽教學 </strong><br />\n<em>*由於模擬器已被ban，以往電腦快刷方法已失效，若仍欲知詳情請自行搜尋(73)或之前嘅post*</em><br />\n首先準備兩部電話or devices<br />\n電話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>係拎黎刷首抽，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">B</span></strong>係拎黎洗走<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>抽完嘅ac<br />\n操作步驟如下：<br />\n<strong>1. </strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">B</span></strong>停喺開波未入game個標題畫面 (即係輸入引繼嗰度)<br />\n<strong>2. </strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>正常入game開ac，skip教學 (打完名一句野都未彈出黎前瘋狂撳抽卡粒掣就skip到)，抽完一次<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">假首抽</span></strong>會更新，更新完就可以拎禮物箱嘅石，開始<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">真首抽</span></strong>，抽完唔啱心水就去右下角settings，撳第二粒掣發行引繼碼<br />\n<strong>3. </strong>拎起<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">B</span></strong>，輸入完引繼碼就會load，跟住繼續停係未入game個標題畫面<br />\n<strong>4. </strong>拎起<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>是旦撳個掣，會彈出error信息話俾你聽ac已經被引繼走，撳完ok後會返回標題畫面，至此為一次首抽流程<br />\n<strong>5. </strong>重複步驟1-4，因為早前已經更新過，第二次打後嘅首抽流程就唔使更新，一分鐘內就能夠完成一次<br />\n<br />\n<strong>首抽建議</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>首抽建議</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/KwIraO7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKwIraO7.png&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=6f7976ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/KwIraO7.png</a>此４角已變時代眼淚，但仍有一定地位, 首抽計搏下面幾隻為佳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AIu98dT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAIu98dT.png&h=4c1ea9d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/120914_c4f610f66f91c47a21d9f5855a039a90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F120914_c4f610f66f91c47a21d9f5855a039a90.jpg&h=26d18140&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65bf4448a5f1d6c6031d07507ab85d9b0bec2d26","tid":534056,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>常見日文辭彙</strong><br />\nキャラクター/ <br />\nキャラ\t----------- 角色 <br />\nチャクラ ----------- 查克拉/卓羅 <br />\nアップ\t----------- Up <br />\nダウン\t----------- Down <br />\nスキル\t----------- 技能 <br />\nタイプ\t----------- 遁 <br />\nダメージ ----------- 傷害 <br />\nスキルダメージ ----------- 技能傷害 <br />\nキャンセル\t----------- 取消 <br />\nランキングイベント ----------- Ranking Event <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>常見辭彙</strong><br />\n<strong>超忍祭/超超忍祭</strong> ----------- 即係限定up，超超忍會有新限定追加<br />\n<strong>祭札</strong> ----------- 每逢超忍抽十連會有一札，夠20札可以去商店換限定券，30札可以自選一隻限<br />\n<strong>P幣</strong> ----------- 只要用1石就會有2個P幣，有時會有多幾倍up，去商店有得換每個月更新嘅角色同其他道具<br />\n<strong>專武</strong> ----------- 角色專有忍具，當配落特定角色時文字描述會變<span style=\"color: red;\">紅字</span>，觸發特別效果<br />\n<strong>PvP</strong>\t----------- 昇級試驗，間唔中會出嘅1對1 event<br />\n<strong>共鬥任務</strong> ----------- lv 1 至 lv 50嘅挑戰任務<br />\n<strong>忍道</strong> ----------- 相同角色自食會升忍道，每升一下會加三圍基礎數値，滿忍道係11/11，滿忍道後可以自選一個bonus ability，暫時大部分角色都係選擇加技速<br />\n<strong>推薦狀</strong> ----------- 用黎升忍道，5星必升，3/4星確率升"},{"pid":"e5884c3a5bad9974959bdb3fafe8605058404253","tid":534056,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>信賴度</strong> ----------- 信賴度係以角色計，並唔係以卡計，如果想儘快升一個角色嘅信賴度，可以全隊入同一個角色嘅卡，最後結算信賴度一樣會全部加入同一個角色<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一關入面隊長得到嘅信賴度係隊員兩倍</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>新手如有其他疑問歡迎發問，一眾巴打會為你解答</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>FAQ </strong><br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 新手抽咩pool開局？<br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 抽開催緊嘅超忍pool，記住唔好抽<span style=\"color: red;\">新手嗰個超忍pool</span>，大伏嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 更新卡住點算? <br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 可以係入game前, 撳右上角引繼隔離個制(ios係引繼下面, 最低果個) ,唔得嘅話就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> load入關卡黑畫面同樣方法 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 唔同機種引繼會唔會冇哂啲石？<br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 唔會 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 新手首抽完有咩做？<br />\n<strong>A.</strong><br />\n1.專武 ------ 去event任務撳概要，睇下而家有冇得打首抽角色嘅專武，要留意大部分任務有限時<br />\n2.上6星 ------ 覺醒首抽角色到6星，曜日任務打覺醒素材同強化素材，6星覺醒素材要去打忍玉<br />\n3.儲石 ------ 打主線任務拎石，屬於次要<br />\n4.刷難關 ------ 大部分關最後都需要40/50體，新手體力最大值未夠可以去商店&quot;アイテム一覽&quot;食拉麵回體，會將你現時用淨嘅體力加上最大值，假設最大值係30體，用到剩20體時再食拉麵就會有20+30=50體<br />\n5.出門靠朋友 ------ 呢個唔使解釋啦掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 傷害點計？ <br />\n<strong>A.</strong> <br />\nType1: 攻擊力% xxx - 攻擊力越高，傷害越大，唔睇對手三圍 <br />\nType2: 倍數傷害 - 攻擊力越高，對手防禦越低，傷害越大。所以減防有用 <br />\nType3: 最大HP% - 扣對手最大HP既xx%，不受自身攻擊、對手防禦影響 <br />\nType4: xxxx點固定傷害 - 完全不受雙方三圍影響 <br />\n注意：加技傷(スキルダメージ)既忍具，可以加以上所有種類技能既傷害<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> Buff會唔會疊加？ <br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 普通buff係計最新果個 e.g. buff攻防40% 再buff攻速30% 結果 = 攻30%防40%速30% <br />\n特殊狀態本身增幅會疊加，而且可以同其他特殊狀態疊加<br />\n例如：奮30% + 開100% + 普通buff30% = 160%<br />\n如果你之後再普通buff 80%，因為呢個係普通buff, 咁就會取代之前果普通buff30% 變成總共 210%<br />\n注意：一般技傷buff係會比遁buff cover, 例如柱間自buff 120%攻+120%技傷, 如果你再上6星舊鳴個buff (80%速+80%風遁），柱間個120%技傷會消失<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. 唔見左ac點算？<br />\nA. <br />\n<br />\nnarucole@help.gree.net （send 去呢到）<br />\n<br />\nゲームのアカウントを復活させたいですけどなかの忍石が __石（仲有幾多石）<br />\nユーザーIDおよびユーザー名：(ID and game名）<br />\n復旧したいデータご利用時に、使用されていた端末情報：(咩手機同咩型號 e.g. iPhone 6 plus)<br />\n最終ログイン日：（最後幾時on）<br />\nゲームを開始された日：（邊日開始玩）<br />\n忍ランク：（衣家幾多level)<br />\n以前に引継ぎコードを発行している場合は、発行したコードとID情報 （之前既引繼碼）<br />\nご登録いただいている場合は事前登録したメールアドレスと特典のコード （有無事前登録？ 沒就打いいえ）<br />\n忍一覧の所持上限数(忍蔵は含みません)：自已忍box total有幾多上限）<br />\n課金された場合はその情報のスクリーンショット（必ず以下のメールが各ストアから送信されます）(有無課金？ 有就cap返張收據 課金會send收據去返你課金個apple email)<br />\n班で編成していた忍の構成内容：(班用緊咩人物）<br />\n所持しているすべての最高レアリティの「忍」名とそれぞれの所持枚数(レアガチャから獲得できものに限る) （有咩限定卡同有幾多張）<br />\neg うちはサスケ［決別の祈り］x1<br />\n波風ミナト［鎮魂の光耀］x1<br />\n直近の「忍石」の所持数 （最後仲有幾多石）<br />\n初めの「レアガチャ」で獲得した「忍」名 （首抽係咩人物 啫係教學完抽果張垃圾卡）<br />\n最後にクリアした「任務」名 （最後完成係咩任務）<br />\n最後に「覚醒」した「忍」名（最後覺醒既卡係邊張）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRanking孖寶：<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0Iy1lqwGfxN4AKDm/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0Iy1lqwGfxN4AKDm%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f896cb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7bukeNcvpLDsCtQ4/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o7bukeNcvpLDsCtQ4%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b2f64e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警世通言 <br />\n咁多位巴打請記住每個月都要發行引繼code，仲要cap低或save幅圖喺其他device到，萬一有咩事都仲有得救</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f379665c51b3953c0e963de29c12aa489cb63f","tid":534056,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"疾風傳拎石條件　<br />\n<br />\n第一章<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170320_add0a1f98055f80a02dc7c7c916d3b9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170320_add0a1f98055f80a02dc7c7c916d3b9a.jpg&h=b7b990d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小櫻入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170321_534bded129ccb4172a137f7de9975c5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170321_534bded129ccb4172a137f7de9975c5c.jpg&h=f128f8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗚門+小櫻入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170321_ba6450900c9f126d342ce03b0d17f0cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170321_ba6450900c9f126d342ce03b0d17f0cd.jpg&h=7f5d0ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗚門入隊<br />\n<br />\n第二章<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170349_915ddf114b5fb3bf6d13d8722a5c02f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170349_915ddf114b5fb3bf6d13d8722a5c02f7.jpg&h=6e29f67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我愛羅入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170349_354c0c7934508a04b3a231570e211fb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170349_354c0c7934508a04b3a231570e211fb7.jpg&h=d633aab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用過武器技能<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/023611_1ab9fa5a0c855771ab46409dc14d4e55.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F023611_1ab9fa5a0c855771ab46409dc14d4e55.PNG&h=55b3c137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡卡西入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170500_0649414faab6bb8868325ede91fe9155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170500_0649414faab6bb8868325ede91fe9155.jpg&h=e8db1646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凱入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170501_f81eca0312b13054ea1186d777daff83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170501_f81eca0312b13054ea1186d777daff83.jpg&h=1bd13360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鳴門入隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三章 (感謝1min60s(一豬)巴提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161751_b1f09ae855d8f10e06a56830c3e335e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161751_b1f09ae855d8f10e06a56830c3e335e0.jpg&h=a0e4299c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161753_3faa402a7a194acae7f69eb6b46ac27e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161753_3faa402a7a194acae7f69eb6b46ac27e.jpg&h=bd2149ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161754_5ba69c9e2fd2bd4e96eb78fb3b44e503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161754_5ba69c9e2fd2bd4e96eb78fb3b44e503.jpg&h=c8fa0f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161754_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161754_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg&h=a9e8100f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161755_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161755_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg&h=41ff80ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(hard mode 通常夠打就夠條件拎石, 如果都係拎唔到可以comment問巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*新手請睇曬post頭先發問*</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5f5bd5cd55e1c7f804ad1c7aade22a072ea032a8","tid":534056,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"給新手的話:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n雖然入到黎見老玩家三句唔埋就屌營運點閪點撚狗, 但呢隻GAME 本身絕對係一個好遊戲, 無論畫風, 操作方法, 平衡性(目前為止)黎講可玩性都算唔錯。GAME名 &quot;collections&quot; says it all, 課金有課金玩法, 無課有無課玩法, 當佢儲卡GAME就好, 罕有角難出係定律黎, N抽唔到限止蝕好緊要, 因為金錢有限, 但限角就會不斷出, 今次追唔到總有一次會出你有愛既角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> That's the meaning of collections<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滿11忍揀技速 記住 記住 記住</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b38400b9c025347788fd3d0d3ec177d191fd85b","tid":534056,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無所屬新手推介＋介紹(濕鳩工程巴提供)</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/053911_4a76456fbcd74a7a3e9b14c05eeba7db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F053911_4a76456fbcd74a7a3e9b14c05eeba7db.jpg&h=b47a1f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新帶土<br />\n新手起手 10／10  實用性10／10<br />\n首先耐性無視可以對應全部關 二來佢唔似舊帶土要全隊無所屬先發揮到op實力<br />\n機本上咩隊都入得<br />\n同埋新手冇忍具 辛苦d滿忍都可以雙閃<br />\n技2扣血 就算無新既排名忍具 用土珠／風土珠可以解決<br />\npvp用黎扑d料理撚又得<br />\n因為泛用性高 所以無所屬黎講佢係最好起手既一隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/051738_1203704de8b4e7a3c7bb195d1fb6b6ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F051738_1203704de8b4e7a3c7bb195d1fb6b6ea.jpg&h=28eb198c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n月讀班<br />\n新手起手 7／10  實用性9／10<br />\n好多新手有個誤解覺得佢打人唔痛 事實佢根本唔係要黎秒人<br />\n佢定位係妨礙角色 同40pain定位唔同<br />\n40pain係半打手半妨礙 月讀班係全妨礙角<br />\n用黎reolad人地條bar／debuff 係打關＆pvp都非常有用<br />\n同時佢組隊都幾彈性 唔需要入無所屬隊就可以發揮實力<br />\n唔好地方係必需旗仔（唔洗滿忍）／求道玉（需滿忍）先達到雙閃效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/053931_042de2e8cf650b80da30053f0e963863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F053931_042de2e8cf650b80da30053f0e963863.jpg&h=1e98bb18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因陀羅<br />\n新手起手 6／10  實用性8／10<br />\n基本上比粒壽紙＋雷珠 <br />\n開下2技就可以閃光 打既傷害極高 而且隊長技實用 容易組隊<br />\n忍具盡量刷粒雷珠就得 因為佢開得因陀羅pool都預左會開埋忍具關比你打<br />\n不過話哂神忍 新手難覺醒<br />\n但總括黎講佢係幾好用既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/053949_f30d83e20fb56f9cd0eb61b817a196aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F053949_f30d83e20fb56f9cd0eb61b817a196aa.jpg&h=25142ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火循班（知）<br />\n新手起手 4／10 實用性6／10<br />\n高傷 純係一隻唔錯既打手 又可以解人buff 同時唔洗入無所屬隊都得<br />\n忍具必需要旗仔 唔係滿忍都雙閃唔到<br />\n不過用查好多 又裝唔到全獸獸個個減查忍具<br />\n所以冇奶媽就唔太建議上場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下其實唔係新手推介 純介紹比有愛組無所屬既人<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n因為我玩火影開始到而家我基本上都係玩無所屬隊 好老實講句 無所屬條路好長<br />\n首先好食忍具 其次好食忍道 最重要係要齊腳 唔係有愛都唔好組無所屬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/054013_18f1b51f1cd74b9b2eb7868f18e98173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F054013_18f1b51f1cd74b9b2eb7868f18e98173.jpg&h=45495dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生日班<br />\n喱隻班用落真係好勁<br />\n素早好快 係好撚快 傷害比火循班低小小 但裝岩忍具<br />\n佢出二下技＝火循班出一下<br />\n可以將火珠既性能完全發揮<br />\n自已又可以裝到全尾獸／新既結印忍具<br />\n用查量唔算多 我相信打pvp算係一隻好煩膠既角<br />\n唯一唔知算唔算缺點<br />\n佢技2要有柱間先完全發揮到 <br />\n但我自已用落就覺得當佢自加100％素早就算 對面有柱間係bonus<br />\n總體黎講係一隻好撚全面既角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/054029_6939941657d4b586e72ed66a184bf457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F054029_6939941657d4b586e72ed66a184bf457.jpg&h=4c1c0e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送既帶土<br />\n喱隻又係一隻好撚正既角色<br />\n佢係一隻support＋妨礙既角色<br />\n2技補100查＋無所屬素早200％ <br />\n推佢素早 比部dv機佢開永動機 成隊變小明<br />\n得閒用下1技 博下封印人又得<br />\n好希望未來會出隻強化版既佢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/054042_fd4feb8db3f150dca02c7a064a707402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F054042_fd4feb8db3f150dca02c7a064a707402.jpg&h=29a4efea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊帶土<br />\n唔多講 冇新帶土先用啦 都唔差既"},{"pid":"ff4a117a2387dca663d8b323a33cf389c5d3faa9","tid":534056,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\">50鳴+曉隊介紹 (by 征龍)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/012602_715dfc122468b09c08d64ad3e9a9481c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F012602_715dfc122468b09c08d64ad3e9a9481c.png&h=1684225e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50鳴 (心) 又叫生日鳴<br />\n<br />\n評分:<br />\n首抽起手: 10/10<br />\n任務:9/10<br />\nPVP: 8/10<br />\n隊長技: 7.5/10<br />\n組隊方面: 冇，咩隊都入得<br />\n<br />\n50鳴係目前數一數二地圖炮，而且必中，新手靠佢一隻可以橫掃好多任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。忍11左就直接雙閃，技速忍具都唔洗，轉用輸出裝更加暴力。技2 黎講一般，buff 3圍100%算唔錯，補查血其實好少，冇專門輔助勁，重點都係技1。打任黎講非常方便而且勁，集高傷、全體、必中、冇卓羅問題於一身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唯一弱點係尾獸type無效(半減都有一定威力)，尾獸無效唯有用技2做support(如果你冇其他更好選擇)。PVP 黎講有一定威力，忍具有魚蛋可以連續3炮清隊，但因為PVP個default setting 係nerf 左好多全體攻，而且對手好多料理撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (打唔入)，再加上佢係50 cost而大部分人pvp都入隻100cost，所以PVP 唔係必選。<br />\n---<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曉隊係傾向PVP。</span><br />\n<br />\n曉隊要員:<br />\n40 pain (技)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/013025_a8b6cd0cb0afff00e5f91c3251dbf4ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F013025_a8b6cd0cb0afff00e5f91c3251dbf4ac.png&h=e85feae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評分:<br />\n<br />\n首抽起手: 6/10<br />\n任務:7.5/10<br />\nPVP: 10/10<br />\n隊長技: 7/10<br />\n組隊方面: 曉隊<br />\n<br />\n40 pain 招技1係曉隊嘅重要控場手段，打全體，高機率reset 行動(番到藍bar前)，低機率中封牢特殊狀態(跑完藍BAR咩都唔做得番去跑藍BAR 幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，卓羅消耗低，最速，忍11 連忍具雙閃。打任黎講一般偏上啦，技2 buff 曉所屬200% skill damage　+ 60 血 ，200%係好高，不過會扣唔係曉所屬嘅角色50% HP；不停技一可以控到人地死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (只要唔係輪迴眼type無效)，不過傷害對比起一線果d就真係低。PVP黎講就神一樣咁濟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，忍11 + 1 件技速忍具做到技1閃光+1 &amp;技2閃光，另外忍具整到第一round 出到技，其他全部小明裝同埋用100 pain做隊長，如此，PVP就做到快過小明，控到對面扔電話落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n40小南 (體)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/013257_d1b336c68fe9e811a3d48ff2b71973e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F013257_d1b336c68fe9e811a3d48ff2b71973e0.png&h=72d8c114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評分:<br />\n首抽起手: 6/10<br />\n任務:8.5/10<br />\nPVP: 8/10<br />\n隊長技: 4/10<br />\n組隊方面: 曉隊<br />\n<br />\n主要定位都係support，雖然技一係耐性無視，但要睇運而且傷害比較低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，通常都係用完技2得閒冇野做先技1。技2 buff 全隊曉100%spd &amp; 100% skill damage &amp;30 %回卓羅，相當勁嘅buff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以打任打pvp 都有地位。不過組隊上有要求(曉)，新手用呢隻起手就預左靠助人打晒，40小南+40 pain 雙限起手會好D。<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n30鼬 (知) 通常叫十拳鼬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/013440_d5dd44df28f0cf40a9557f761ed2b769.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F013440_d5dd44df28f0cf40a9557f761ed2b769.png&h=319b89d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評分:<br />\n首抽起手: 7/10<br />\n任務:8/10<br />\nPVP: 10/10<br />\n隊長技: 3/10<br />\n組隊方面: 冇，咩隊都入得<br />\n<br />\n十拳鼬 被動有半減查，忍具有多50% 就可以做到永動0查出技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。技1 耐性無視+ 高機率封印，但用完減70%血。勁在傷害真係好高，而且唔洗任何前置技能，直接出技1 就做到秒殺般傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，負作用遠遠冇想像中咁高。技2 debuff 3圍70% + 幻，幻狀態可以令人地番去跑藍bar，不過機率幾低下。打任要睇total 有幾多關同幾多隻人，愈多就愈唔適合，因為扣好多血，十拳係打速攻，不過呢個問題都容易解決，入100 pain / 40 pain 補血，不過始終係打單體，打任清場冇全體咁快。PVP 方面因為可以雙閃+耐性無視+冇查問題+本身就小明+技1直接秒人一條命，相當好用而且勁，封印係添頭，有時有奇效(例如封住對面隻煩膠40pain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )。 技2 有時都會用黎PVP，不過就睇機率降同降D咩，不如技1 直接打直接解決問題，打任要黎降防降速打傷害任，不過debuff 有更好選擇，重點都係技一。"}]}